<quantity box="[1014,1092,268,294]" metricMagnitude="4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" unit="km" value="25.0">25 km</quantity>
from Kabul, on the road to Jalalabad and Peshawar.
</paragraph>
